        "notes": "Hotjar Events API call for lead session tagging. Kept as Custom HTML on purpose: Hotjar has no GTM-native Event tag, and the unofficial Knowit Experience 'Hotjar Event' Community Template (https://github.com/gtm-templates-knowit-experience/gtm-hotjar-event) requires an authoritative cvt_* ID and galleryReference signature that this skill cannot fabricate. If you want to switch, install the template from the GTM Gallery first, export the resulting container, and copy the Knowit cvt_* ID + galleryReference block in. Includes the window.hj queue shim per references/hotjar.md so the call survives if it fires before the base script finishes loading. Hotjar Events carry no parameters - the event name is the only payload. Available on Observe/Ask Plus, Business, and Scale plans."
